## What does Cometly include?

### What features does every Cometly plan include?

- **Multi-touch attribution** — first, last, linear, U-shaped models
- **Full-funnel customer journey tracking**
- **AI Ads Manager** — automated recommendations ("scale this campaign, cut that one")
- **AI Chat** — natural-language data queries and analysis
- **CAPI enrichment (Conversion Sync)** — improves Meta match rates from ~4.5 to 9.4
- **Comet Pixel** — first-party tracking that bypasses ad blockers
- **No-code dashboards**
- **Conversion API integrations** — Meta, Google, TikTok
- **Email and SMS attribution**
- **Organic source tracking**
- **Dedicated onboarding and support**

### What features are Enterprise-only?

- **Two-Way API access** — push/pull data programmatically
- **Custom integration builds**
- **Dedicated onboarding team**
- **Solutions engineer support**
- **Unlimited client workspaces** (Agency plan)

