## What are Cometly's hidden costs?

### Why is Cometly's pricing hard to find?

The pricing page uses "contact sales" for most tiers, and conflicting pricing structures exist across review sites. You can't confidently budget for Cometly without a sales conversation. Compare this to competitors who publish pricing transparently.

### How much more do you pay as ad spend grows?

Like Triple Whale's GMV trap, Cometly charges more as your ad spend grows. When you're spending more on ads — the exact time you need attribution most — Cometly's cost scales with you. A brand growing ad spend from $50K to $200K/month could see Cometly costs triple.

### Can you export Cometly data?

Only on the Enterprise tier (~$5,000/mo). If you want to pull Cometly data into your own BI tools or data warehouse, you need Enterprise. On lower tiers, you're limited to Cometly's built-in dashboards.

### Are Cometly's AI features limited on cheaper plans?

Lower-tier plans may have limited AI Chat credits. The core AI features that differentiate Cometly could be partially gated on cheaper plans.

### Does Cometly track organic and content channels?

Cometly tracks paid ads (Meta, Google, TikTok) and some organic/email sources, but it's fundamentally an ad attribution tool. If organic search, content marketing, or referral traffic drive significant revenue, Cometly has limited visibility into those channels.

