## Is Cometly worth the price?

Cometly's CAPI enrichment is genuinely unique — if you spend heavily on Meta Ads and need to improve match rates, this single feature can justify the cost. The AI Ads Manager provides actionable recommendations for paid media teams.

The main concerns are pricing opacity and ad-spend-based scaling. If you need all-channel attribution (not just paid ads) or prefer transparent pricing, alternatives like mbuzz ($29-299/mo flat) and Triple Whale (free tier available) offer attribution without the opacity.

